the Ninja Dropouts.

67
00:06:05,449 --> 00:06:06,784
So that's what happened...

68
00:06:09,369 --> 00:06:11,955
–Gantetsu!
–Gantetsu, are you all right?

69
00:06:12,039 --> 00:06:13,916
You're not hurt, are you?

70
00:06:13,999 --> 00:06:15,501
I'm glad you're ok.

71
