taking care of them.

74
00:06:26,970 --> 00:06:30,599
Gantetsu is just like
the central figure of a family.

75
00:06:32,392 --> 00:06:33,602
I can't believe this...

76
00:06:34,269 --> 00:06:37,397
You mean that...the kid who
was there just now was...

77
00:07:11,974 --> 00:07:14,268
Akio!!

78
00:07:29,533 --> 00:07:31,660
Where are you going...Gantetsu?!

79
00:07:33,829 --> 00:07:35,455
To the Ninja Dropouts' hideout.

80
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:40,419
I'm gonna get...Akio back!

81
00:07:40,502 --> 00:07:45,424
I will get Akio back! Your only job
is to guide me there!

82
00:07:45,507 --> 00:07:46,884
Don't interfere!

83
00:07:46,967 --> 00:07:49,595
Todoroki, I understand how you feel.

84
00:07:49,678 --> 00:07:52,431
However, Gantetsu saved Akio
and all these other kids

85
00:07:52,514 --> 00:07:55,058
from the Ninja Dropouts!

86
00:07:55,142 --> 00:07:57,102
Besides, there's something
you should do before that!

87
00:07:57,186 --> 00:07:58,270
Don't mess around with me!

88
00:07:58,979 --> 00:08:04,193
Even so, this guy...Gantetsu...
is a member of the Ninja Dropouts.

89
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:07,613
The Ninja Dropouts killed my parents!

90
00:08:09,698 --> 00:08:11,617
You're absolutely right.

91
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:13,952
My own crime will never
be washed away.

92
00:08:17,414 --> 00:08:21,960
As soon as I get Akio back...
you can...do whatever you like to me!

93
00:08:25,339 --> 00:08:26,757
I'm going, too!

94
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,175
Me, too!

95
00:08:28,258 --> 00:08:31,011
Then, Sakura, please look
after the children!

96
00:08:31,094 --> 00:08:32,179
Leave it to me!

97
00:09:01,875 --> 00:09:02,876
Todoroki...

98
00:09:03,377 --> 00:09:08,090
I've continued hating that guy
for five years...

99
00:09:16,265 --> 00:09:17,975
