Damn it!

101
00:09:23,772 --> 00:09:26,692
In any case, we've got to take care
of your little brother right now!

102
00:09:26,775 --> 00:09:27,859
I know that!

103
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:32,072
This time for sure...
I'll rescue Akio!

104
00:09:46,461 --> 00:09:48,672
Where did you stash our treasure?!

105
00:09:50,424 --> 00:09:53,176
Where's your hideout?!

106
00:09:56,722 --> 00:09:58,140
Come on! Talk!

107
00:09:59,808 --> 00:10:02,811
I'll never...tell you!

108
00:10:02,894 --> 00:10:05,063
You little brat!

109
00:10:12,654 --> 00:10:15,365
That's the Ninja Dropouts' hideout...

110
00:10:18,744 --> 00:10:21,747
That residence belongs
to Shura, the leader.

111
00:10:22,372 --> 00:10:24,499
I'm pretty sure that's where Akio will be.

112
00:10:26,877 --> 00:10:27,961
Akio...

113
00:10:32,090 --> 00:10:34,551
Oh! Hey! Todoroki! Wait!

114
00:10:34,634 --> 00:10:35,927
Damn!

115
00:10:46,813 --> 00:10:49,066
This ain't good! They'll detect us!

116
00:11:06,917 --> 00:11:08,126
Leaf Hurricane!

117
00:11:09,669 --> 00:11:11,463
Let me handle this situation!

118
00:11:12,506 --> 00:11:13,924
I leave it to you, Bushy-Brows.

119
00:11:19,221 --> 00:11:20,722
Akio!

120
00:11:20,806 --> 00:11:21,890
This way.

121
00:11:24,309 --> 00:11:28,230
I'm pretty sure that Akio is
being tortured in the basement...

122
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:32,526
That guy was once a Ninja.

123
00:11:32,609 --> 00:11:34,403
There's no telling what
he'll try to do.

124
00:11:36,738 --> 00:11:38,115
I'll go first.

125
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:54,798
Akio!

126
00:11:54,881 --> 00:11:56,049
W-Wait!

127
00:11:56,133 --> 00:11:57,717
Akio...!

128
00:12:00,554 --> 00:12:02,013
Gantetsu...!

129
00:12:02,097 --> 00:12:03,140
You jerk...!

130
00:12:03,223 --> 00:12:04,433
Don't come over here!

131
00:12:07,686 --> 00:12:08,895
Gantetsu!

132
00:12:08,979 --> 00:12:10,021
Akio!

133
00:12:10,105 --> 00:12:11,940
Hey! Gantetsu!

134
00:12:16,194 --> 00:12:19,114
So only one animal got caught
in the net, huh...?

135
00:12:19,197 --> 00:12:20,615
Shura!

136
00:12:20,699 --> 00:12:25,203
He's one stubborn brat.
He never unsealed his lips.

137
00:12:25,287 --> 00:12:28,206
I'll use another method to
get back the treasure.

138
00:12:28,707 --> 00:12:31,126
After I've killed the lot of you!

139
00:12:54,983 --> 00:12:56,902
