144
00:13:46,409 --> 00:13:48,620
Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu.

145
00:14:31,871 --> 00:14:33,248
Todoroki, you take care of Akio!

146
00:14:45,468 --> 00:14:46,720
Todoroki!

