that's how you protected Akio...

152
00:16:18,436 --> 00:16:21,523
Yet I... I...!

153
00:16:49,300 --> 00:16:50,969
Gantetsu! Give me Akio!

154
00:16:59,436 --> 00:17:03,189
Elder brother...
you came to rescue me, after all...

155
00:17:03,273 --> 00:17:05,275
Hang in there, Akio!

156
00:17:06,192 --> 00:17:09,946
My elder brother...
Todoroki, it's really you, isn't it?

157
00:17:40,393 --> 00:17:42,771
This spells the end of the Ninja Dropout.

158
00:17:42,854 --> 00:17:43,897
Yeah...

159
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:45,148
That's right.

160
00:17:47,108 --> 00:17:48,985
But where is Naruto?

161
00:17:49,903 --> 00:17:51,738
Hey!

162
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:56,326
Naruto Uzumaki! On the scene...!

163
00:18:02,999 --> 00:18:04,709
Naruto! Lee!

164
00:18:05,585 --> 00:18:07,045
Akio!

165
00:18:07,128 --> 00:18:09,631
Akio's back!

166
00:18:10,131 --> 00:18:11,341
It's Akio...!

167
00:18:12,175 --> 00:18:14,177
Are you all right, Akio?!

168
00:18:14,260 --> 00:18:15,261
Yeah...

169
00:18:15,345 --> 00:18:17,180
Oh my gosh, you're hurt!

170
00:18:17,263 --> 00:18:20,433
I'm fine. It's nothing!

171
00:18:20,517 --> 00:18:23,436
Sakura, could you
take care of his wound?

172
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,896
Leave it to me.

173
00:18:27,148 --> 00:18:28,274
Take care of him.

174
00:18:34,739 --> 00:18:38,243
Apologies for the inconvenience...
Let's head to the capital.

175
00:18:45,792 --> 00:18:47,836
I just cannot forgive you.

176
00:18:48,837 --> 00:18:52,549
But it is true that you rescued Akio.

177
00:18:56,094 --> 00:18:58,054
The Ninja Dropouts
have been annihilated.

178
00:18:59,055 --> 00:19:00,849
Gantetsu got caught up
and died in the fighting

179
00:19:00,932 --> 00:19:02,892
that ensued while being escorted.

180
00:19:04,894 --> 00:19:06,104
Elder brother...

181
00:19:07,021 --> 00:19:08,231
Todoroki...

182
00:19:12,735 --> 00:19:16,739
Yeah! Great! That's great!

183
00:19:23,580 --> 00:19:24,747
You're gonna stay here, right?

184
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:26,541
Huh?

185
00:19:27,417 --> 00:19:31,671
You're gonna stay here with Gantetsu
and the other children, right?

186
00:19:36,384 --> 00:19:38,469
I haven't been a good brother...

187
00:19:39,304 --> 00:19:42,849
But you are an irreplaceable
elder brother for those children.

188
00:19:44,642 --> 00:19:45,643
Elder brother...

189
00:19:51,024 --> 00:19:52,108
What's this...?

190
00:19:52,775 --> 00:19:54,068
This is the souvenir that

191
00:19:54,152 --> 00:19:55,236
I didn't have a chance to
give you back then.

192
00:20:00,199 --> 00:20:03,244
Elder brother... Thank you.

193
00:20:13,421 --> 00:20:15,340
Let's go! Ninja!

194
00:20:15,423 --> 00:20:16,424
Okay!

195
00:20:16,507 --> 00:20:18,927
–Good bye!
–Good bye!

196
00:20:19,010 --> 00:20:20,929
–Take care, everyone!
–See you!

197
00:20:21,012 --> 00:20:26,726
–Bye!
–See you!

198
00:20:41,407 --> 00:20:43,451
Hey... How are we gonna
get out of this forest...

199
00:20:43,534 --> 00:20:46,663
without Gantetsu?!

200
00:20:46,746 --> 00:20:48,206
We can't go back now!

201
00:20:48,289 --> 00:20:51,209
We took this path earlier
on too, didn't we...?

202
00:20:51,292 --> 00:20:52,961
I'm starving...

203
00:20:53,044 --> 00:20:54,879
I can't go on.

204
00:20:56,631 --> 00:21:01,803
Hey! Somebody rescue us!

205
00:21:05,556 --> 00:21:10,103
The Key to the rusted heart's door

206
00:21:10,186 --> 00:21:16,067
Will always be smiling right near by

207
00:21:21,781 --> 00:21:26,327
Even if rains of spears were to fall,
I will run through it

208
00:21:26,411 --> 00:21:31,040
Because I want to find the joy
without a shape

209
00:21:31,124 --> 00:21:35,545
This big dream of mine that
cannot be translated to words,

210
00:21:35,628 --> 00:21:40,550
I will make it come true,
even if it were to deepen my wounds

211
00:21:40,633 --> 00:21:45,346
We stand here today because of
what we believed through,

212
00:21:45,430 --> 00:21:50,018
That is why I will continue running forward,
never looking away

213
00:21:50,101 --> 00:21:54,397
Even if I'm told that
there is no bright future

214
00:21:54,480 --> 00:22:01,487
I'll change it right away,
lighting it with all my feeling

215
00:22:01,571 --> 00:22:05,867
The wind is probably testing our hearts

216
00:22:05,950 --> 00:22:10,580
In my heart, I gently grasped my hands

217
00:22:10,663 --> 00:22:15,334
You are probably searching for
the answer to your tears

218
00:22:15,418 --> 00:22:20,173
Your dream is always waiting near by,
with the answers in its hands

219
00:22:20,256 --> 00:22:24,719
The Key to the rusted heart's door

220
00:22:24,802 --> 00:22:30,558
Will always be smiling right near by

221
00:22:37,315 --> 00:22:39,734
Naruto, what on earth were you thinking?

222
00:22:39,817 --> 00:22:42,445
What? I only brought an injured person
to the hospital.

223
00:22:42,528 --> 00:22:44,572
But to bring an outsider
into the village...

224
00:22:44,655 --> 00:22:46,991
But I'm sure he is not a bad guy at all.

225
00:22:47,075 --> 00:22:49,410
I understand your feelings,
but he has amnesia.

226
00:22:49,494 --> 00:22:51,537
There is a possibility that
he's an enemy spy.

227
00:22:51,621 --> 00:22:52,622
Please, Grandma.

228
00:22:52,705 --> 00:22:54,832
I'll make an exception,
just this one time.

229
00:22:54,916 --> 00:22:58,294
But you will be his keeper, and will be
held accountable for all his actions.

230
00:22:58,377 --> 00:22:59,378
That's all.

231
00:22:59,462 --> 00:23:01,672
